    <h1>Multi-Channel Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">Reaching customers through multiple independent channels — email, social, search, paid ads, direct mail. Gives prospects multiple discovery paths and reduces the <strong>single-channel dependency risk</strong> that kills businesses when algorithms change.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
